Package: conseguiR
Type: Package
Title: Integrative Germline, Somatic, and Epigenomic Graph Prioritization
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Pranav", family = "Mishra", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "pranav.mishra@yale.edu"),
    person(given = "Mark", family = "Robinson", role = "aut", email = "mark.robinson@yale.edu")
    )
Description: Tools for scoring somatic, germline, and epigenomic evidence at genes and regulatory elements,
    projecting scores onto biological graphs, running diffusion, calling subnetworks, and exporting results for
    downstream visualization and app development.
